	<description>
		<![CDATA[
			<p>This is a responsive, HTML5 template for Joomla! 2.5 from <a href="http://kisswebdesign.co.uk">KISS Web Design</a>.</p>
			<p>It follows the <a href="http://www.w3.org/TR/mobile-bp/#OneWeb">'One Web'</a> philosophy - designing websites that can be delivered to all screens and devices, present and future</p>
			<p>It is based on <a href="https://github.com/twitter/bootstrap">twitter/bootstrap</a> version 2.1.0</p>
			<p>Prior to creating this template KISS Web Design forked twitter/bootstrap and created our own <a href="https://github.com/KISS-Web-Design/bootstrap">baseline bootstrap</a>.</p>
			<p>This template is taken from our baseline, not the original twitter/bootstrap</p>
		]]>
